long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the mystical world of Black Myth: Wukong every time you open a new tab! This Chrome extension combines powerful imagery of Wukong with an elegant, user-friendly design. Perfect for fans of chrome live wallpapers, this chrome wallpaper brings the iconic Wukong right to your screen, enhancing your browsing experience with a sense of adventure.

Explore the extension’s features designed to elevate your new tab:

Live Wallpaper: Stunning Wukong scenes in motion
Clock and Date Display: Easily keep track of the day and time
Google Search Bar: Direct access to Google, built-in for convenience
Adjustable Shortcuts: Add or remove sites to match your workflow

Seamlessly blending epic visuals with useful tools, this chrome background extension is crafted for true fans of Wukong’s legend. Let each new tab inspire you with a glimpse into the mythic journey.
